import altair as alt
from vega_datasets import data

cars = data.cars()

alt.renderers.set_embed_options(theme='dark')

alt.Chart(cars).mark_line().encode(
  x='Horsepower',
  y='Miles_per_Gallon',
  color='Origin'
).properties(
    width=700,
    height=300
)


from time import sleep

for i in range(100):
    print(i)
